{"tid":2329286,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒙面便衣警追截男生 認不見被告曾向巴士噴漆 鄭念慈在上午審訊後將被告還柙","createTime":"2020-12-17T06:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:41:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a803f0f6cace3e9e579162725451f3772b694d2","tid":2329286,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"去年12月，土瓜灣有學生快閃堵路，蒙面便衣警埋伏監視，當場拘捕四名中學生，有14歲女生被制服後遭女警「當凳坐」，引起公眾嘩然。其中一名被捕16歲男生疑藏伸縮棍，案件今早開審。男生承認非法集結罪，但否認刑事損壞及管有攻擊性武器兩罪；裁判官鄭念慈取消擔保，男生須還柙應訊。便衣警作供時承認，當日沒有看見被告對巴士噴漆，不過「較早前見到另一班人咁做，我有理由相信喺同一夥人，先作出拘捕」。<br />\n<br />\n16歲鄭姓被告被指於去年12月4日在土瓜灣馬頭圍道近譚公道參與非法集結，並與其他人損壞屬於九巴有限公司一架巴士的擋風玻璃，同時攜有一支金屬伸縮棒，被控非法集結、刑事損壞及管有攻擊性武器三罪。被告今承認非法集結罪，但否認其餘兩罪。裁判官鄭念慈在上午審訊後將被告還柙。<br />\n<br />\n警員徐家俊供稱，當時駐守紅磡警署特遣隊，在馬頭圍道一帶喬裝埋伏，進行反堵路行動，其間接報指有人在譚公道聚集，疑似準備堵路。<br />\n<br />\n惟徐觀看巴士車頭攝錄片段後，在盤問下承認片段中向車頭噴漆的三人中不包括被告，又承認被告沒有向巴士噴漆。徐及後在控方覆問時解釋：「較早前見到另一班人咁做，我有理由相信喺同一夥人，先作出拘捕。」鄭官最後直接問徐有否在現場看見被告噴漆，徐謂：「見唔&hellip;&hellip;唔肯定。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/PENWGDF3RJAMRNXP62UFRJUILU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FPENWGDF3RJAMRNXP62UFRJUILU%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28R4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=2c8a8d36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FPENWGDF3RJAMRNXP62UFRJUILU%2F&h=dbf647c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/PENWGDF3RJAMRNXP62UFRJUILU/</a>"},{"pid":"28a8b117d1a3d7f63dd0bd23c511551c05202a6c","tid":2329286,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19fbb2ebe63e7008fbaf137b2e2169c94cc70ef","tid":2329286,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"根本就亂鳩咁拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c597ebe546aaa868b0c8db01e4093cbbc427388a","tid":2329286,"uid":8439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"好撚正 坦白認鳩拉都無事"},{"pid":"29866532c25c48482393545d0dda095bebd001d1","tid":2329286,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8369b8922f38016fc3eff7183e565446a6d57846","tid":2329286,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"被告今承認非法集結罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb161f2dc2d298f8f2e2022fb5a4a99662e3985","tid":2329286,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"鳩砌生豬肉都無成本 仲有就係未判坐住監先"},{"pid":"8068898d51d32375e0990399d3ccbbdfbfed5749","tid":2329286,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8369b8922f38016fc3eff7183e565446a6d57846","tid":2329286,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"被告今承認非法集結罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"斷正 當場拉 認左坐少d"},{"pid":"105dccecf608c9efbefc45c50db170d68e6fdc7e","tid":2329286,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8369b8922f38016fc3eff7183e565446a6d57846","tid":2329286,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"被告今承認非法集結罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"上次九月答辯已認,但另兩項唔認<br />\n<br />\nSeptember 15<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9425&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28R4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=5f042733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9425</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#張天雁裁判官 <br />\n #1204土瓜灣 #答辯<br />\n<br />\n鄭（16）<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)參與非法集結<br />\n被控於2019年12月4日在九龍城土瓜灣道農圃道與馬頭圍道交界參與公安條例18(1)條屬非法集結<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️‼️認罪‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n(2)刑事毀壞<br />\n於同日同地與男子卓、李、女子徐及其他不知名人士無合法辯解損壞一輛九巴巴士UW9615的擋風玻璃<br />\n<br />\n❌不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n(3)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n於同日同地管有一支伸縮鋼棒<br />\n<br />\n❌不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n辯方希望在審訊時才一併處理控罪一的案情，因與控罪二、三有關連<br />\n<br />\n5位控方證人，警誡下被告的說話無爭議<br />\n辯方除了被告沒有其他證人<br />\n<br />\n預審期：2天<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年12月17-18日0930九龍城法院進行中文審訊，期間以現有條件保釋✅"},{"pid":"72b4298ddfe0de9dd15c1381056c003f72abc2f9","tid":2329286,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8068898d51d32375e0990399d3ccbbdfbfed5749","tid":2329286,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8369b8922f38016fc3eff7183e565446a6d57846","tid":2329286,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"被告今承認非法集結罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"斷正 當場拉 認左坐少d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"呢條罪都幾撚好笑，幾條友行街就告得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b1ed80efeb2607c3634f5efc3bec09862654db","tid":2329286,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:02:27.000Z","msg":"唔好再認罪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a90fba0a2c8a23ee47f80b095c2375d8b51d2c","tid":2329286,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b4298ddfe0de9dd15c1381056c003f72abc2f9","tid":2329286,"uid":20291,"